    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/17e5c8c3b68205fd57dc7f5b0fbdae26.avif?t=1744567426\" width=600 height=67 /></span>在“Iosis”中，您将控制“Silver Guard”，保护“Vitriol Vessel”免受污染金属的袭击。主要的伤害来源是动量：速度和质量越高，伤害越大。在快节奏的运行中，您将有机会根据几个主题改善自己的游戏风格，聚焦于移动性、自我牺牲、操纵等方面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/24d5c214aa9caa3193826108c6a1d172.poster.avif?t=1744567426\" width=766 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/24d5c214aa9caa3193826108c6a1d172.webm?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/24d5c214aa9caa3193826108c6a1d172.mp4?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Iosis”受到弹幕射击和塔防游戏的启发，特别强调可自定义运行，从而产生独特的构建。作为“Silver Guard”死亡只是暂时的挫折，这将解锁取决于自我伤害并释放毁灭性力量的构建。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/92b02933d46ac838cd58a4b36a78f50b.avif?t=1744567426\" width=800 height=962 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/67f70119f535288bacfc66945d67ef6f.avif?t=1744567426\" width=600 height=67 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>基于碰撞的近战：</strong> 核心战斗取决于玩家动量作为主要伤害来源，即移动速度越快，造成的伤害越大。成为一个大型物体也是增加你的伤害输出的一种方式，但要注意不要过度限制自己的机动性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/60e5db1ac1dc33966800bb6d715c9aa0.avif?t=1744567426\" width=800 height=370 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>超过 60 个收藏品升级：</strong> 在“Iosis”中，可收集的升级品分为两类：主动的“法术”和被动的“残留物”。残留物的类型各不相同，包括参数化升级、周期性激活效果、基于碰撞和冲刺运动的触发效果等。法术更加多功能，可以在运行过程中拿起和放下，以自定义您的构建。<br></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>超过 20 种不同的敌人：</strong> 有许多不同类型的金属敌人，铁、铜、汞等，每种敌人都专门针对一种游戏玩法。您需要制定防御机制来抵消它们的战斗优势。<br></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>3个线性渐进阶段：</strong> 游戏的净化分为三个层次：门、喷泉和塔。您将发现随着游戏难度的逐渐增加，您需要不断提高自己的技能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/f80dd16328e1ea8e1d3b5ca10d76087f.poster.avif?t=1744567426\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/f80dd16328e1ea8e1d3b5ca10d76087f.webm?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/f80dd16328e1ea8e1d3b5ca10d76087f.mp4?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>独特的环境挑战：</strong> 随着您在炼金空间中的不断进展，您将遇到不同的环境，这些环境都会带来独特的挑战并奖励永久的升级。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/50e1f12f4b8751b01a299a2e2542d2a7.poster.avif?t=1744567426\" width=618 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/50e1f12f4b8751b01a299a2e2542d2a7.webm?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2097170/extras/50e1f12f4b8751b01a299a2e2542d2a7.mp4?t=1744567426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，您将扮演一位守护者，守护着实现净化的关键物质——绿矾，通过炼金空间的不同阶段实现净化和升华。您将面对各种贪婪的基础金属，它们试图污染绿矾，因为所有金属都有一个渴望到达最纯净的黄金。您的主要防御来源是您的动量，通过移动和力量，您必须寻求更高的智慧和净化。</p>",
